text: Aleksey Silayev (born 4 January 1984) is a Russian ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill event at the 2002 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Russian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Russia Category:Ski jumpers at the 2002 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Nizhny Novgorod
